Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}んっ
